                <p>No matter how far you go,</p>
                <p>Your heart will always bring you back.</p>
                <h4>Verse 3:</h4>
                <p>It’s just another Bad Day.</p>
                <p>I’m here with you</p>
                <p>To protect you, to care more for you.</p>
                <p>You just need to trust</p>
                <p>That everyone can truly love.</p>
                <p>Everything reminds me of you.</p>
                <p>When I look at the stars,</p>
                <p>I see them shining, forming,</p>
                <p>Drawing your initials in the night sky.</p>
                <h4>Verse 4:</h4>
                <p>Sometimes we end up disappointing.</p>
                <p>I feel like I wasn’t everything you expected.</p>
                <p>Without your presence inside,</p>
