                    <strong> Title:</strong>

                        <strong>just Me</strong>

                <p>The nights went by so fast,</p>
                <p>We don’t need to pretend anymore</p>
                <p>That we were happier than ever.</p>
                <p>We’ve already reached our limit.</p>

                <p>Now you can go places</p>
                <p>Without making up excuses,</p>
                <p>And spend sleepless nights.</p>
                <p>Screw the flowers sent every morning,</p>
                <p>That won’t make me forget.</p>

                <p>You thought you’d get away this time,</p>
<p>You don’t need me anymore.</p>
<p>You won’t miss me</p>
<p>When I’m no longer around.</p>
<p>But it’s fine, you don’t care,</p>
<p>Just like you won’t care</p>
<p>About anyone crossing your path.</p>

<p>I still had hope in you,</p>
<P>I noticed it as time went by,</P>
<P>Because nothing changed in you.</P>

<P>You were like a drug</P>
<P>When you chose someone else.</P>
<P>Now you’re trying a new chapter,</P>
<P>But I still receive flowers.</P>
<P>It must be hard to move on,</P>
<P>Even with someone new.</P>
<P>But I don’t care anymore.</P>


---

<P>Clorus</P>

<p>Because now it’ll just be me,</p>
<p>Only me, and no one else.</p>
<p>I hope that one day you become better,</p>
<p>That all the harm you caused me</p>
<p>Returns to you, with many thorns.</p>
--

<p>We were falling apart,</p>
<p>You’re just another guy who conquers</p>
<p>And then destroys everything in sight.</p>
<p>Everything we had is left behind.</p>


<P>I tried in every way to make us happy</P>
<P>But it was never enough; you wanted more.</P>
<P>You don’t have to be this way,</P>
<P>Just become better to live.</P>
<P>Don’t let this destroy your life.</P>

<P>We drifted apart</P>
<P>Because it was best for both of us.</P>
<P>The summer dreams, postponed,</P>
<P>Will now have new voices to tell them.</P>

<P>When you’re crying,,</P>
<P>Your tears will dry too,</P>
<p>Just like mine did.</p>
<P>When you chose someone else.</P>

<P>When your heart is on fire,</P>
<P>There’ll be someone new to put it out.</P>
<P>I hope that one day you become better.</P>
<P>You thought you’d get away this time,</P>
<P>You don’t need me anymore.
<P>You won’t miss me</P>
<P>When I’m no longer around.</P>
<P>But it’s fine, you don’t care,</P>
<P>Just like you won’t care,</P>
<P>About anyone crossing your path.</P>

